==English==

===Etymology 1===
From Latin ''[[periodicus]]'' or French ''[[périodique]]
// From Greek ''[[περίοδος]]'' which is ''[[περί-]]'' + [[οδός]]

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɒdɪk|-ɒdɪk]]

====Adjective====
{{en-adj-notcomp}}
# [[Relative]] to a [[period]] or periods.
# Having [[repeat|repeated]] [[cycle|cycles]].
# Occurring at [[regular]] [[interval|intervals]].
# Pertaining to the [[revolution]] of a [[celestial]] object in its [[orbit]].
# [[Periodical]].

